{"tid":2113278,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［考古］點解王菲首歌叫紅豆？","createTime":"2020-07-18T04:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T05:03:37.000Z","uid":113637,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5e111da2f8f8a802ec526c2faff9dcff5eaeb4","tid":2113278,"uid":113637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:11:24.000Z","msg":"點解點解點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽左咁多年都理解唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n莫非夕爺鍾意食紅豆沙？"},{"pid":"26135df1b06b4e696fc56110adcd0228ac32009c","tid":2113278,"uid":199776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"紅豆生南國"},{"pid":"acf13ff9e56433c19c8e0e83837456aae7bc8d0b","tid":2113278,"uid":146574,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cd5e111da2f8f8a802ec526c2faff9dcff5eaeb4","tid":2113278,"uid":113637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:11:24.000Z","msg":"點解點解點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽左咁多年都理解唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n莫非夕爺鍾意食紅豆沙？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"除粵語地區外，許多人最初接觸王菲，應該都是從一些國語歌開始，《紅豆》便是其中之一。許多人因王維的「願君多採擷，此物最相思」而知道紅豆的相思之意，所以覺得這首《紅豆》也是表達相思。<br />\n<br />\n其實不然，林夕本人曾寫過，《紅豆》中，紅豆只是歌詞的中一件幫助表達的道具。選擇寫紅豆，是因為那時正在看日劇，裏面木村跟女朋友面臨分手，女朋友神不守舍地把一鍋紅豆粥煮爛，對這幕戲非常深刻。而紅豆本身有相思之意，熬爛了，真有點血肉模糊的纏綿感。所以才會把紅豆作為題目。顯然，「紅豆」只是詞中一個襯托情感的意象，而不是情感的物質載體。那麼，這首歌里詞人想表達什麼內容，我們一起分析一下。<br />\n<br />\n《紅豆》是典型的「菲式情歌」。曲作者柳重言在創作之初想像了一下王菲會如何演繹這首歌后，很短時間內就創作出了曲子，可以說這是為王菲量身定製的作品。因此，哀怨淒冷是這首歌的最大特點，在分析時以一位哀怨女子的角度入詞顯然更易理解。"},{"pid":"a8e0945617bb4a17be80bfc194d54c1d446260ab","tid":2113278,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:13:22.000Z","msg":"此物最相思"},{"pid":"c1407fd7b8142dc1110fb92f4cdc6d36b61e31cb","tid":2113278,"uid":64193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"「紅豆生南國，春來發幾枝，願君多採擷，此物最相思」唐代著名詩人王維的這首五言絕句《相思》"},{"pid":"6e084ce4ace42d0ab248f8d60f96a42e6ee98636","tid":2113278,"uid":113637,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"原來我文化水平真係好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e149fa4a8740122ed18646c9a21edf9dd6961c","tid":2113278,"uid":47669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:34:37.000Z","msg":"王菲真係唱得好好聽"},{"pid":"3c0812760309f4dd580808199a97d96d873baa72","tid":2113278,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6e084ce4ace42d0ab248f8d60f96a42e6ee98636","tid":2113278,"uid":113637,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"原來我文化水平真係好低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"唔係你低<br />\n<br />\n林夕中文系 不嬲識好多野<br />\n<br />\n平時唔出聲者"},{"pid":"379bfc22a310e4ef57670396d83df620928684b8","tid":2113278,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:42:41.000Z","msg":"油鼓好 油鼓好"},{"pid":"f78e1aebb30075e9cd0fc6ffc1ba2bd9880493bb","tid":2113278,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2e149fa4a8740122ed18646c9a21edf9dd6961c","tid":2113278,"uid":47669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:34:37.000Z","msg":"王菲真係唱得好好聽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DrSb_wihVQY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDrSb_wihVQY&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiYbsTeectjBlsojPGU